{
  "stem": "24212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was the kapo who was distributing with a sort of half globe-shaped dish she was distr-- or sometimes she had a ladle.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she would take it from the top, so you got nothing swimming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when Lily came around, then she would reach lower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Or she would say, Lily, wait until I get to the bottom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were the goodies-- the potato peels or vegetables or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Meat, very seldom.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then when we were in, in the-- in Gross-Rosen and where we were on work kommando, we got better food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also that was already '44, '45, and the Germans were getting a hell of a beating.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the moment that the news from the front was bad for the Germans, we were better off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because the German supervisor suddenly became human and brought us a piece of bread or maybe a half rotten apple or a potato.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We could tell how the war is going by the behavior of the German supervisor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When they started kicking us and, and, and cursing us and being rough with us, we knew the Germans are winning again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe just one battle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when the, the tide turned, suddenly they were nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Insurance, you know, took out the insurance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I brought a prisoner an apple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'm not a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appels, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well first of all, they started at dawn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the time it was still dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was true with Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was true in the tunnel, all over the place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they woke up us at 5:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then appel started at 6:00.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For no good reason, because we didn't start marching to the factory except maybe a few minutes before 7:00.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And work started at 7:00.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
